text:
Located at Camp Road, off Tanglin Road, in a quiet lush greenery is Camp Road Interim Park. It's a green space for everyone. The park hold a log-theme Fitness Corner, a children playground, and swings.
It also have a special Swing for wheelchair bound person. A children log playground. There is a small, dog run area complete with washing area and a drinking water fountain.
Because of the relatively inaccessibily, the small serene park is mainly used by the residents around the area.
Nice and quiet along tanglin road. Lots of people walking their dogs on a weekday sucha good life.
